data.description: This home is located in a 24 hour guard gated community.  It includes 1 pool with jacuzzi, 2 children parks, and a gated tennis court.  This home has an open floor plan with 3 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms an a loft that can be easily converted into another bedroom space.  It has high ceilings, custom shutters, custom soft close kitchen cabinets with waterfall kitchen island and quartz countertops.  It has Thermador stainless steel appliances, built-in wine cooler and a pullout panty.  The Laundry room has been updated with custom cabinets and quartz countertops, the washer and dryer are included in the sale of the home.  The first floor includes built-in seating in dining room with engineered hardwood floors.  The master bedroom and loft have custom closets. There is built-in custom desk in the loft area. Also, there is a Tesla car charger located in the 2 car attached garage for electric car charging.  This home is located in a cul-de-sac of the gated community so there is limited traffic. It is walking distance to the architecturally award winning SoFi Stadium, home of the super bowl champion Los Angeles Rams and Charges adjacent to Los Angeles Forum.  SoFi Stadium will host the 2026 World Cup and 2028 Olympics.  The other adjacent corner is the home of the new Clippers Arena which makes this a rare gem for the sports enthusiast.  Also, next to SoFi Stadium is Hollywood Park casino and NFL headquarters.  There are numerous restaurants in the area and a Movie theater is the SoFi Complex.  This home is a rare find, don't let this opportunity pass by.
